Swastika Temple Wololo Tankcopter was created/rendered by Thobie Buntaran a.k.a. Loreng on 15 September 2021, Mantrijeron, Yogyakarta, Indonesia.

The Wololo Tank, mainly used for gold, glory, and gospel domination campaign on another habitable planet. A Holy Temple Swastika was originally designed by Loreng from Santuari Lab, which had begun work in 3000 on a new multi-rotor Tankcopter. In the 3020's this celestial beast was mainly utilized to transport the Santuarian Sadhu Warriors from their Santuari Monastery to the battlefields. Equipped with non-lethal golden ammunitions, this AirLand specialist can turn disloyal opposing enemy units with their golden bullets.  

Aggressively maneuvering on-air & land battles.
Gorgeously sitting in your digital galleries.
